            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.611</ph> Contract clause.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2126e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2140e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049995.dita#i1049995"
                        base="i1049995"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.232-17</xref>, Interest, in solicitations and contracts unless it is contemplated that the contract will be in one or more of the following categories:</p>
					          <ol id="d2126e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracts at or below the simplified acquisition threshold.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracts with Government agencies.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracts with a State or local government or instrumentality.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e57" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracts with a foreign government or instrumentality.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e66" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracts without any provision for profit or fee with a nonprofit organization.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e76" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(6)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Contracts described in <xref href="FAR-i1120403.dita#i1120403"
                              base="i1120403"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  5.5</xref>, Paid Advertisements.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2140e88" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(7)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Any other exceptions authorized under agency procedures.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2140e99" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer may insert the FAR clause at <xref href="FAR-i1049995.dita#i1049995"
                        base="i1049995"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.232-17</xref>, Interest, in solicitations and contracts when it is contemplated that the contract will be in any of the categories specified in <xref href="#i1081984"
                        base="i1081984"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.611</xref>(a).</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
